    ('PHIL-P 200', 'PROBLEMS OF PHILOSOPHY', '14337', 'Class Status', 'MW Monday, Wednesday 11:10 AM–12:25 PM', 'JH 001', 'Sadie McCloud', 1, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'BIOLOGY BUILDING', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Important problems at the center of rational reflection upon human experience, including issues in ethics, aesthetics, political philosophy, philosophy of religion, metaphysics, epistemology, and/or the history of philosophical thought. Emphasis upon interpretation, critical analysis, and evaluation of philosophical texts from contemporary and/or historical perspectives. Topics vary. Introductory level.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd A&H credit
COLL (CASE) A&H Breadth of Inquiry credit'], NULL),
