    ('PHIL-P 242', 'APPLIED ETHICS', '9022', 'Closed', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 5:30 PM–6:45 PM', 'BH 206', 'Jag Williams', 0, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'BALLANTINE HALL', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Application of moral theory to a variety of personal, social, and political contexts, such as world hunger, nuclear weapons, social justice, life and death decisions, and problems in medical ethics.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd A&H credit
